class="container"><h2 id=fAQs class="section-heading">FAQs:</h2><div
class="row"><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-much-does-it-cost-to-open-a-brewery class="question">How much does it cost to open a brewery?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>Brewery start-up costs depend on the initial size of the brewery. Microbrewery startup costs can range from $100,000.00 to over $1 million, according to our research. If you are wondering how to start a brewery with no money, it is virtually impossible since you need so much equipment.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-do-i-start-a-brewery-legally class="question">How do I start a brewery legally?</h3><div
class="answer"><ul><li><a
href="#choose-a-name-and-trademark-it">Choose a name</a>.</li><li><a
href="#write-a-business-plan">Create a business plan</a>.</li><li><a
